column5: how is the fishing up at goderich? i just want to know if anyone knows the numbers i usually go in october.
As I recall,..it all starts on october 7 at precisely 6:43 in the am,...no fish before then,..tons everywere in the river after.  check the Regs tho.
Booking the time off work now.  But if I can't get there before 7:00 do you think there will be any left?   lol.

You already missed the run man, they like the low, warm and clear summer waters!  Nahh just messin man, take a drive up there and fish, if they are there catch them and don' tell anyone. Less fishing pressure
nah i already got my salmon so i will want steelhead or whatever just askin how the runs are... lake huron is a bit later than most places
